These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, ambient, blues, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, indonesian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, biathlon, lacrosse
1. the german is the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is not the fan of folk##6
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the german##6
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
7. the nigerian is somewhere between the fan of blues and the polish##7
8. the person who's sport is baseball is between the fan of ambient and the fan of blues##2
9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | techno      | ambient   | folk  |
| Nationality   | german    | indonesian   | nigerian | polish  |
| Sport         | lacrosse | baseball | biathlon     | water-polo |

