.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, fanta, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: papaya, cabbage, lemon, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, russian, italian, dutch
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating cabbage##6
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating lemon##1
 5. the person eating papaya is the italian##1
 6. the person eating lemon is the dutch##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the russian##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person eating pomegranate and the person drinking fanta##7
10. the italian is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | mirinda         | fanta    | soy-milk  |
| Food          | pomegranate     | cabbage | papaya | lemon |
| Nationality   | australian     | russian     | italian  | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, drawing, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, egyptian, british, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, ship, scooter
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
4. the italian is between the french and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the scooter##6
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the egyptian##7
7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
9. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | photography | drawing  | rock-climbing  | sudoku |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | british | italian | french     |
| Transport     | scooter    | tram     | motorbike     | ship         |

