.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, indie, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, french, german, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, van, scooter, trike
1. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
2. the french is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the fan of pop is the person driving the van##1
5. the german is the fan of r&b##1
6. the colombian is the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
8. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the fan of pop and the fan of indie##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | classical     | r&b   | indie      |
| Nationality   | french    | colombian | german | egyptian  |
| Transport     | van | skateboard  | trike    | scooter |

