.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, soy-milk, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, techno, indie
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, lizard, goldfish
1. the person drinking sprite is not the fan of indie##6
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the fan of ambient##7
3. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person drinking juice##7
5. the person drinking juice is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the lizard is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice  | sprite | soy-milk | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | indie | techno  | r&b  | ambient    |
| Pet           | goldfish | turtle  | pony    | lizard    |

