.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, reading, baking, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, american, australian
1. the australian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the australian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the american is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##7
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the mexican##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | hot-chocolate | almond-milk        | sprite       |
| Hobby         | baking | singing    | reading | camping |
| Nationality   | australian     | dutch  | mexican    | american   |

