.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, videographer, dressmaker, project-manager
4 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, pony, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, car, jet-ski
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the pony##2
4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
7. the dressmaker is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
| Job         | videographer | dressmaker | mechanic    | project-manager |
| Pet         | rabbit      | cat | fish       | pony         |
| Transport   | car | jet-ski    | skateboard | tram     |

