.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, writing, chess, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, fantasy, family
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the owner of the horse is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 7. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person watching family movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
10. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | reading | writing      | chess | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | drama | disaster  | family       |
| Pet           | mouse         | horse       | goldfish    | frog  |

