4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, bird, cat
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person eating cauliflower##7
5. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
9. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | nectarine  | orange  | cauliflower | cherry   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | epic | spy     | western   |
| Pet           | ferret | snake       | bird      | cat |

