.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-14::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, orange, potato, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, weightlifting, cricket, ice-hockey
1. the fan of country is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the fan of pop##7
2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the fan of country##7
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
5. the person eating potato is on the right of the fan of blues##1
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the fan of country##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
8. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
9. the person who's sport is cricket is not the fan of blues##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | broccoli | radish | potato          | orange  |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | blues      | country    | pop   |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby  | cricket | ice-hockey |

