1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
2. the person eating banana is not the person watching thriller movies##6
3. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching disaster movies##7
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
8. the person watching epic movies is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
9. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food          | plum   | banana  | pomegranate     | kiwi    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | epic | disaster      | thriller |
| Sport         | baseball | lacrosse     | weightlifting | surfing       |

