.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, chess, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, bartender, firefighter, designer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, spy, action
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
2. the scientist is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the designer##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
8. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
9. the firefighter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the scientist##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess | dancing   | reading | collecting |
| Job           | bartender     | designer | firefighter   | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster         | spy        | adventure  | action   |

