.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, accountant, security-guard, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, disaster, musical, crime
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, guinea-pig, goldfish
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the chef##1
 2. the security-guard is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the security-guard is on the right of the accountant##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person watching disaster movies##6
 5. the chef is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 6. the chef is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the security-guard is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | doctor  | chef | accountant | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | musical     | romance      | crime    |
| Pet           | pony    | goldfish      | guinea-pig     | rabbit  |

 